{"title":"MUE_Emergencias_Diabeticas","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/MUE - Medicina de Urgencia/MUE_Emergencias_Diabeticas.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"EMERGENCIAS DIABETICAS EN URGENCIA","guid":"73Ml5MC7Q9ikR966AwbEJA","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"CETOACIDOSIS DIABETICA (CAD)","guid":"Hcnl16z8QAu_PzT_-Vljiw","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Definicion","guid":"eW6gqzVvSRCnAeheAz1QFw","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"Hiperglicemia + acidosis metabolica + cetonemia","guid":"98-VJ9SjT0eVxpnKFSsTwA","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"2","text":"Triada: glicemia >250 mg/dL + pH <7.3 + cetonas (+)","guid":"5JzL2_u0QSuzbPSSu5-Oaw","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"2","text":"Brecha anionica elevada (>12 mEq/L)","guid":"ktYmWsb1Tri1LHxLVUDCfg","children":[]}]},{"id":"6","parent":"1","text":"Clasificacion de gravedad (ADA)","guid":"f7hCv_RjTa2htEU-5uWv4A","children":[{"id":"7","parent":"6","text":"LEVE → pH 7.25-7.30, HCO3 15-18, alerta","guid":"gUgUeQ2pQpKZAl-YN16aew","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"6","text":"MODERADA → pH 7.0-7.24, HCO3 10-14, somnoliento","guid":"OFyCPkx3QWeHd3RgiY2njg","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"6","text":"SEVERA → pH <7.0, HCO3 <10, estupor/coma","guid":"Te8QLtDpR_mmwMIbqWmrSA","children":[]}]},{"id":"10","parent":"1","text":"Fisiopatologia","guid":"SbOb3gSAS_yBq1ZteD1Hkg","children":[{"id":"11","parent":"10","text":"Deficit absoluto o relativo de insulina","guid":"VanvBSR2Tf6_5argfkFynQ","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"10","text":"Hormonas contrarreguladoras ↑ (glucagon, cortisol, GH, catecolaminas)","guid":"rzpKVwflR5q2987-TWb2AA","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"10","text":"Lipólisis → AGL → cetogenesis hepatica","guid":"CvdxAeJZQtGV5CbFUMycyA","children":[{"id":"14","parent":"13","text":"Acetoacetato, beta-hidroxibutirato, acetona","guid":"R2DLBgpoRUOr-3dXU6eMIA","children":[]}]},{"id":"15","parent":"10","text":"Gluconeogenesis y glucogenolisis ↑","guid":"Q6ycL2e5TuudKbyKCGVywA","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"10","text":"Diuresis osmotica → deshidratacion severa","guid":"xlfWz3z3Scm65Qb1bU96mg","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"10","text":"Deficit hidrico promedio 5-7 L","guid":"9P3Ex9_-RjOl8vZKPaRI5Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"18","parent":"1","text":"Epidemiologia en adulto mayor","guid":"YkupFEvHR4eMMNmbssVEig","children":[{"id":"19","parent":"18","text":"CAD en DM2 → 34% de casos (no solo DM1)","guid":"mPFYrSZuTq2c3rY8vW_j7g","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"18","text":"Mayor mortalidad en >65 anos → 50% de muertes por CAD","guid":"H3thR4k6QM-I63highcntQ","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"18","text":"Infeccion como precipitante mas comun en AM","guid":"MKPOVM67Syy03c0jROCStg","children":[]}]},{"id":"22","parent":"1","text":"Desencadenantes (5 I)","guid":"PybD_3bIRiikH8tKCJ2svg","children":[{"id":"23","parent":"22","text":"Infeccion (30-40%) → neumonia, ITU, sepsis","guid":"YtC6Hru_S5Oi50rfRHMKHQ","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"22","text":"Incumplimiento tratamiento insulinico","guid":"bwiuKAjQT86uf-J1I_Hw9w","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"22","text":"Infarto (IAM, ACV)","guid":"QJsrRnJTRFiOK5bzoob8gg","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"22","text":"Inicio de diabetes (debut)","guid":"SefnqIE5T4-pVZsHz74WOQ","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"22","text":"Ingesta de farmacos → corticoides, iSGLT2","guid":"llSUom5aT7eO753PKiQ0Dg","children":[{"id":"28","parent":"27","text":"PERLA → CAD euglucemica por iSGLT2","guid":"C__W0YCmT_WmQF40BR4pfQ","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"27","text":"Glicemia normal o levemente elevada","guid":"yhAwhJaHQ8OmwQsy5dPPIw","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"27","text":"Alta sospecha si iSGLT2 + acidosis + cetonas","guid":"CwpMMkk-Qt-6GpmRjcQH7A","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"31","parent":"1","text":"Presentacion clinica","guid":"8jF9SeWjTeyeDilZ1_U9Lw","children":[{"id":"32","parent":"31","text":"Poliuria, polidipsia, perdida peso","guid":"MgG3cj5cSwGkqHCmjhX8ig","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"31","text":"Nauseas, vomitos, dolor abdominal","guid":"IH4CSAyDT4KYRn-k_HSz2g","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"31","text":"Respiracion de Kussmaul (rapida, profunda)","guid":"UAUCY2zaTPChqaJJUdZGzQ","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"31","text":"Aliento cetonico (frutal)","guid":"hUVVLzlQSMaNwNI_wINXEQ","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"31","text":"Deshidratacion, taquicardia, hipotension","guid":"tN9IBRzARuOPPus7g3fNkw","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"31","text":"EN ADULTO MAYOR","guid":"S9hLqs2IS2-aSWq8u1TNqQ","children":[{"id":"38","parent":"37","text":"Sintomas menos clasicos","guid":"_QBXyWc-RLKMokm9LkkjkA","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"37","text":"Confusion/delirium como presentacion principal","guid":"7kF5uvsPRoWMunCsa1QqIw","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"37","text":"Dolor abdominal puede simular abdomen agudo","guid":"Z19fKKQ1QyCg3GUXMh2Lng","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"37","text":"Kussmaul puede estar ausente si debilidad muscular","guid":"9zcLo-UqSU-clROd5ocS5A","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"42","parent":"1","text":"Laboratorio","guid":"WDx1Rqy9Qe6zsJzeTVc3RA","children":[{"id":"43","parent":"42","text":"Glicemia → generalmente >250 mg/dL","guid":"6K8XHgvITRC3fuWkd_XQZQ","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"42","text":"Gases arteriales → pH, HCO3, pCO2","guid":"h3nAZjafT9azSqwM_xj92g","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"42","text":"Cetonas → beta-hidroxibutirato (preferido) o cetonuria","guid":"qBHB6g0kQX2SwbsVRgcUaA","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"42","text":"Electrolitos → Na, K, Cl, brecha anionica","guid":"KxVc-yLDSxeXwQOkz8euNg","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"42","text":"SODIO CORREGIDO → Na + 1.6 por cada 100 mg/dL de glicemia >100","guid":"RBJx56HPTl2uoH36s1lfwg","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"42","text":"POTASIO → puede estar normal/alto pese a deficit corporal total","guid":"DEv6ZTY3QDaPo5nQ2uS6FQ","children":[{"id":"49","parent":"48","text":"K <3.5 → reponer ANTES de insulina","guid":"2S-8CtoqRTy6nLm4axSEFg","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"48","text":"K 3.5-5.3 → reponer con fluidos","guid":"GjgHJNKWTz2TmK_ZauV-Ww","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"48","text":"K >5.3 → no reponer, monitorizar","guid":"TX2mpJxPRs2mbbI_DQiMBQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"52","parent":"42","text":"BUN, creatinina, osmolaridad","guid":"yhl4OM-AS6-YWW2zHmQAZA","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"42","text":"Hemograma, PCR, lactato","guid":"EPFKdvY9RsWKXczFFTJOxw","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"42","text":"ECG (descartar IAM como precipitante)","guid":"4hD4sKchT2yH09HSmd8NBw","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"42","text":"Rx torax si sospecha neumonia","guid":"F7lgL9tXSzuvwZ5Ppy3kJg","children":[]}]},{"id":"56","parent":"1","text":"Manejo","guid":"i9huBywYTS6TSXM7bdFdSA","children":[{"id":"57","parent":"56","text":"FLUIDOS → prioridad #1","guid":"EEtt33I7Qb6qLDNSWXBgvA","children":[{"id":"58","parent":"57","text":"SF 0.9% → 1-1.5 L primera hora","guid":"7MnPPtYFSLWJtRnnTfeeZw","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"57","text":"Luego 250-500 mL/h segun estado hidratacion","guid":"sqIWuMkOSN6_8UPyc6EtKA","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"57","text":"Cambiar a SF 0.45% si Na corregido >145","guid":"VHqU1XwwR6GBoySlJFSLdg","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"57","text":"Agregar SG 5% cuando glicemia <250","guid":"Tzcq6tUZTFaLcghlCXC-FA","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"57","text":"EN ADULTO MAYOR → velocidad reducida","guid":"uI97FCIzQ_etleOpb1ZkQw","children":[{"id":"63","parent":"62","text":"Riesgo de edema pulmonar","guid":"VYecd6OnRyi2ykGiHbIT4Q","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"62","text":"Monitorizar PVC o ecocardio si duda","guid":"IzoWrtbvT7-vUUOASdVbSg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"65","parent":"56","text":"INSULINA","guid":"NI3j06aRSz6H0VKjeI1amA","children":[{"id":"66","parent":"65","text":"Bolo 0.1 U/kg IV (opcional, no obligatorio)","guid":"HingaLwvRJmkTHWoYU92cw","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"65","text":"Infusion 0.1 U/kg/h (o 0.14 U/kg/h sin bolo)","guid":"k4ef1wGwQKalzFplumYT4g","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"65","text":"Meta → descenso glicemia 50-75 mg/dL/h","guid":"4WKRmOU9S6OQoC6_aZqRIA","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"65","text":"Cuando glicemia <250 → reducir a 0.02-0.05 U/kg/h","guid":"jcgyWVuoTfGxaOR5l2URkw","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"65","text":"Agregar SG 5% para mantener glicemia 150-200","guid":"MPsfVkmNQvy1YalrFwX5Gw","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"65","text":"NO suspender infusion hasta resolver cetoacidosis","guid":"09eePIppTVeclFpS1EQABQ","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"65","text":"PERLA → NO iniciar insulina si K <3.5","guid":"BytixSWfSaWF9lTGMCUjtQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"73","parent":"56","text":"POTASIO","guid":"pGVydP__T1emTMenMW4HtA","children":[{"id":"74","parent":"73","text":"Deficit corporal total 3-5 mEq/kg","guid":"Ff62IiJuRPe2JhynnBEsfg","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"73","text":"K <3.5 → 20-40 mEq/h (retrasar insulina)","guid":"R3KlSJvmR0mYQsMUhMyMMw","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"73","text":"K 3.5-5.3 → 20-30 mEq/L en fluidos","guid":"BJNu1M5pQ5KiaU6ta2hfFQ","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"73","text":"K >5.3 → no agregar, medir cada 2h","guid":"d8eHuN88RqKUEfUeOP-Ktw","children":[]}]},{"id":"78","parent":"56","text":"BICARBONATO","guid":"geCPEz6xSOWE9GJ1qQblzw","children":[{"id":"79","parent":"78","text":"SOLO si pH <6.9 (controversia en pH 6.9-7.0)","guid":"jXxLWOBRQyKiY37K5dEjSA","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"78","text":"NaHCO3 100 mEq en 400 mL + 20 mEq KCl en 2h","guid":"6_FY6tlgQ2ahbccDY18lEQ","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"78","text":"No indicado rutinariamente","guid":"bzdp9TMNR9ugY4tpZKdMyQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"82","parent":"56","text":"FOSFATO","guid":"eMmE2ISWSlySi6AylE2eIA","children":[{"id":"83","parent":"82","text":"Reponer si <1.0 mg/dL","guid":"kz18_0a9R4-zXIDtzZR0lQ","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"82","text":"O si disfuncion cardiaca/debilidad muscular","guid":"ZoShP0cRQmiRXCYLIEC2rg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"85","parent":"1","text":"Criterios de resolucion","guid":"PBi3wYs0SVCUE5qOgycQ-g","children":[{"id":"86","parent":"85","text":"Glicemia <200 + al menos 2 de:","guid":"QwiV7RD2SSm0E5-7Ul1GYw","children":[{"id":"87","parent":"86","text":"pH >7.3","guid":"Oa6hdhRxQpqFaOHG-QdFSQ","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"86","text":"HCO3 ≥15","guid":"2ApR59-GTH6P4ANwnhAJfw","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"86","text":"Brecha anionica ≤12","guid":"H78843wjR1ae0AcAKukKVg","children":[]}]},{"id":"90","parent":"85","text":"Transicion a insulina SC → solapar 1-2h con infusion IV","guid":"ljGXdFzXSH64AJ_MvjfSfg","children":[]}]},{"id":"91","parent":"1","text":"Complicaciones del tratamiento","guid":"_Yyk_c_QSR2ioQng5El2-Q","children":[{"id":"92","parent":"91","text":"Hipoglicemia (si insulina excesiva)","guid":"YU6fNlgYRzaWxaHInD_P6g","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"91","text":"Hipokalemia (si no reposicion adecuada)","guid":"3ZekbR50SRy2h9SRpfwxQQ","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"91","text":"Edema cerebral (raro en adultos)","guid":"AjG3F6w-Qa-PyjgZYeP93A","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"91","text":"Sobrecarga hidrica (riesgo en AM con IC)","guid":"7p_B2fpRSBuwBZtkqSayVw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"96","parent":"0","text":"ESTADO HIPEROSMOLAR HIPERGLICEMICO (EHH)","guid":"t1650c0wQvS0vOcY5QIoyA","children":[{"id":"97","parent":"96","text":"Definicion","guid":"h7H1eEVySSyD7shp7exV4A","children":[{"id":"98","parent":"97","text":"Hiperglicemia severa + hiperosmolaridad + deshidratacion","guid":"yIpRMQpDQzqMbiAHFVTv_g","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"97","text":"SIN cetoacidosis significativa","guid":"vqsl6DX3R0SD4N5c9Vp0zQ","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"97","text":"Guia JBDS 2023 (Mustafa, PMID:36370077)","guid":"UX6_n-dcR0mJWjnHy7r4Xg","children":[]}]},{"id":"101","parent":"96","text":"Criterios diagnosticos","guid":"mfggouPzQPmdIvCUzqPYEw","children":[{"id":"102","parent":"101","text":"Glicemia >600 mg/dL","guid":"-0