,"children":[]},{"id":"120","parent":"115","text":"Cirugía, trauma","guid":"h-C0GDrRR5uDbPznwMt1AQ","children":[]},{"id":"121","parent":"115","text":"Debut DM2 en adulto mayor","guid":"E7KtXK5DR6Cbdgh5zOnWJg","children":[]}]},{"id":"122","parent":"96","text":"Presentacion clinica","guid":"dcypX0nFSV29cBkKlGWMng","children":[{"id":"123","parent":"122","text":"Poliuria, polidipsia (dias a semanas de evolucion)","guid":"k2X5Q_p_Q5SM1TN2UWqCWQ","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"122","text":"Deshidratacion severa","guid":"MR50x6AZRxyF7K5b_dAyzw","children":[]},{"id":"125","parent":"122","text":"Alteracion de conciencia → desde confusion a coma","guid":"kFkChKy2Tf60Nlg8DKyP7Q","children":[{"id":"126","parent":"125","text":"Correlaciona con osmolaridad","guid":"4f6cWx5ORPKojGaKjXF7_Q","children":[]},{"id":"127","parent":"125","text":"Osm >340 → letargia/estupor","guid":"YwVRSrvNQLC2ipLO6tE7HQ","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"125","text":"Osm >360 → coma","guid":"GEC6eLl0SuGTCPf8Pt6oDw","children":[]}]},{"id":"129","parent":"122","text":"Focalidad neurologica → puede simular ACV","guid":"O25VUA7wQYuQjQJtiodjgg","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"122","text":"Convulsiones (hasta 25%)","guid":"PrLWsB2ZT_6eTjYcoV8Lqg","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"122","text":"Hipotermia","guid":"R4o_U1CYSYGEA7qJYkcNdA","children":[]},{"id":"132","parent":"122","text":"EN ADULTO MAYOR → puede ser primera manifestacion DM2","guid":"gr_L4EAWQI-hzf49qk3eWg","children":[]}]},{"id":"133","parent":"96","text":"Laboratorio","guid":"-nGZDoR4SO-_xCuuLbCnZQ","children":[{"id":"134","parent":"133","text":"Glicemia → frecuentemente >800-1000 mg/dL","guid":"DcPQFFbJR-6LFIGG_xYXAg","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"133","text":"Osmolaridad calculada → 2xNa + glicemia/18 + BUN/2.8","guid":"SssL-jz_Tg-9WfvEThwZGA","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"133","text":"Osmolaridad efectiva → 2xNa + glicemia/18","guid":"nggML6ZhSSqPA32UEVailQ","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"133","text":"Deficit hidrico = 0.6 x peso x (1 - 140/Na corregido)","guid":"lFCWX7p2RGy6EJyYGa-hZQ","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"133","text":"Sodio corregido → Na + 1.6 por cada 100 sobre 100","guid":"6_oEq-anQ3a-OSTXRG9WUQ","children":[]},{"id":"139","parent":"133","text":"Funcion renal → IRA prerrenal comun","guid":"WDJ7c8wjR5WfWliuxxO_Yg","children":[]},{"id":"140","parent":"133","text":"Buscar precipitante → cultivos, ECG, TAC cerebro","guid":"cHN_1urGQ1yBG9lsai-JnA","children":[]}]},{"id":"141","parent":"96","text":"Manejo","guid":"u0ynmBcmR5CDtLn0fGFi0w","children":[{"id":"142","parent":"141","text":"FLUIDOS → MAS AGRESIVO que en CAD","guid":"c5jUoWZdSgOJeJpukm8uJg","children":[{"id":"143","parent":"142","text":"SF 0.9% → 1-1.5 L primera hora","guid":"xL0nWJDRSVWldj0cKHeSkg","children":[]},{"id":"144","parent":"142","text":"Meta: reponer 50% deficit en primeras 12h","guid":"TVEZv6AVRey0fckoyzBS6w","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"142","text":"Resto en siguientes 12-24h","guid":"cs5C8cC0TcOmTLT1XofpJw","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"142","text":"EN ADULTO MAYOR → balance cuidadoso","guid":"SVpgT6ErRceqXwMSLqBU6g","children":[{"id":"147","parent":"146","text":"IC previa → monitoreo hemodinamico estrecho","guid":"Lj1oq3yqSqGnWA18Qdm6dA","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"146","text":"Meta: descenso osmolaridad 3-8 mOsm/kg/h","guid":"9jb0gqiaRUOThbRcecJCaw","children":[]},{"id":"149","parent":"146","text":"Descenso demasiado rapido → edema cerebral","guid":"1INVRx4gRFqAUel0DtrxQQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"150","parent":"141","text":"INSULINA","guid":"iEZi_aIcThS2ftYN3uhDPg","children":[{"id":"151","parent":"150","text":"Iniciar SOLO cuando glicemia deja de descender con fluidos","guid":"HyskdDC5TV6R6MohMZpSFQ","children":[]},{"id":"152","parent":"150","text":"O inmediatamente si cetonas significativas","guid":"d47hzLJJTEW0SQc4P-QLog","children":[]},{"id":"153","parent":"150","text":"Dosis menor que en CAD → 0.05 U/kg/h","guid":"FKeEEi6OQmKblvERLNFlow","childr