:"JVoyOVcPTQGe7-8d9m8n-w","children":[]},{"id":"172","parent":"170","text":"Nivel 2 → glicemia <54 mg/dL (clinicamente significativa)","guid":"1Bz3cab3Q9SEwpfNRnCs7w","children":[]},{"id":"173","parent":"170","text":"Nivel 3 → evento con compromiso cognitivo severo","guid":"WRQcS9-5StCFJ5yC6lf3ng","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"174","parent":"167","text":"Epidemiologia en adulto mayor","guid":"CLYGXPvoQsmI5JOApCLz9g","children":[{"id":"175","parent":"174","text":"Causa mas frecuente de consulta por emergencia diabetica","guid":"nVFm0GZLQ1u16EKG_iqJ8Q","children":[]},{"id":"176","parent":"174","text":"Incidencia ↑ con edad avanzada","guid":"rCaTn_ncTGaXitdEKYCdWA","children":[]},{"id":"177","parent":"174","text":"Lee 2018: hipoglicemia severa → ↑ eventos CV y mortalidad (PMID:29127240)","guid":"3MdK1s_KQNeU9_7Mn4o8gA","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"174","text":"Burgess 2023: DM y caidas en AM (PMID:37612537)","guid":"lfjHbJb4TkWanniJcyAOhg","children":[]}]},{"id":"179","parent":"167","text":"Causas en adulto mayor","guid":"W0_LhsheTZ6rKXNj2KMhag","children":[{"id":"180","parent":"179","text":"Sulfonilureas → PRINCIPAL causa en AM","guid":"b-b89Cq6Ta2i8Y_9dnIaLQ","children":[{"id":"181","parent":"180","text":"Glibenclamida → MAS peligrosa (accion prolongada)","guid":"syR-G4iYRhS855FHvaFCmg","children":[]},{"id":"182","parent":"180","text":"PERLA → evitar glibenclamida en >65 anos","guid":"L-jWB2eYTW2tIVagRxilag","children":[]}]},{"id":"183","parent":"179","text":"Insulina → errores de dosis, omision comida","guid":"RUEuT8jqQniAbgYa0EmDEA","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"179","text":"Insuficiencia renal → acumulacion farmacos","guid":"tcsjlW5TSRaZdkbd1IGe3Q","children":[]},{"id":"185","parent":"179","text":"Insuficiencia hepatica → menor gluconeogenesis","guid":"Ca5i4GCfQi6iHwq2-DoKAw","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"179","text":"Desnutricion/sarcopenia → menores reservas glucogeno","guid":"00NcOmhSS-C3T4nfZvYnLA","children":[]},{"id":"187","parent":"179","t